scheduled_activities.description: Core. Cardio. Strength. This workout is designed to target all major muscles groups. Work towards a healthier mind and body as you stay active during your week with this energetic class. No matter your experience or fitness level this class is for you.

Discover varying terrains while riding along to a unique playlist. Each instructor brings a different style to their class to give you a different challenge each ride. Cycle Fit is meant to make you sweat, increase your heart rate and have fun! Perfect for new and advanced riders.

This workout uses resistance training with high repetitions to activate fast twitch muscle fibers. You will grow strong, lean muscle mass and enhance your athleticism. The calorie burn won’t just stop after the class is over - your lean muscle fibers will keep you burning calories for long after you’ve left!

This easy to follow Latin-inspired dance fitness class will sculpt and tone your body with non-stop, calorie burning, and high-energy fun! This class is great for all and brings together movement and music for an exciting workout! No dance experience required.

This class emphasizes precise movements to activate, isolate, and stabilize core muscles. This class is great for improving posture, flexibility, balance and strength, to help you stay strong throughout your workweek. The class is a mixture of beginner and intermediate exercises and options will be given for all levels.
Join Rowena Whey, drag queen and spin instructor, and work up a sweat in a spin class fueled by all your favourite diva anthems. Featuring drag performances, and a whole lot of energy and sass!

This class will work your entire core foundation with unique exercises, drills, and balance training. Learn new moves to help sculpt your core, glutes, and total body. This class is designed for all fitness levels. Don't be afraid to sweat!

This easy to follow Latin-inspired dance fitness class will sculpt and tone your body with non-stop, calorie burning, and high-energy fun! This class is great for all and brings together movement and music for an exciting workout! No dance experience required.

Explore a gentle, yet powerful series of postures and breathing techniques that promote physical strength, flexibility, and mental clarity. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced practitioner, Hatha Yoga offers a balanced approach to cultivate inner peace, enhance mindfulness, and restore harmony to your being. Join us and experience the transformative benefits of Hatha Yoga for overall well-being and vitality.

Get prepared to get energized and sweat to the beat of the music through high intensity interval training (H.I.I.T) and tempo segments. This workout will feature different positions on the spin bike to utilize different muscle compartments for a more overall body workout. Lights off, Sweat on!

Inspired by elements of ballet, yoga, and Pilates, this class focuses on low-impact, high-intensity movements designed to strengthen your body and give you long lean muscles. You’ll use low-weight and high repetitions. No dance experience required.

Work at your own pace as your instructor takes you through a series of both strength training and cardio full body movements that’ll have you sweating and your muscles burning. With a variety of exercises in each session you will leave feeling strong and accomplished!

Challenge yourself with this great cardio conditioning class! Instructors will lead you through a variety of challenging rides including hills, sprints and team riding all set to great motivating music. Suitable for all levels of riders.

Strengthen, stretch, and sweat in this hatha-based yoga class that incorporates meditation and breath-work with classic yoga poses. With variations offered in each pose, you'll learn the foundations of yoga and find opportunities to challenge yourself in new ways. Suitable for all participant levels.

NOTE: This class is only open to students in the Society of Graduate and Professional Students (SGPS).
